content: अनागम {%<ab>a.</ab>%} {@--1@} Not come, not present. {@--2@} [न. ब.] (In law) Without the title-deed or document of possession (such as purchase deed &c.), anything possessed from time immemorial and without any documentary proof; °उपभोगः enjoyment of property without such a deed. --मः {@--1@} Non-arrival. {@--2@} Non-attainment.
